        <h2>Support Calm, Resilient Skin in Your 40s</h2>
        <p class="light-gray">
          In your 40s, combination skin becomes more vulnerable to sensitivity, redness, and visible signs of aging.
          Hormonal changes, environmental factors, and a weakening skin barrier can contribute to chronic redness and
          irritation. This NicholsMD skincare routine combines powerful antioxidants, soothing botanicals, and
          barrier-supporting treatments to reduce visible redness and reinforce skin health. Perfect for combination
          skin balancing oiliness and dryness while addressing sensitivity and aging concerns.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="result__first__row">
        <div class="result__description__container">
          <p class="light-gray">Your Essential Skincare Set for Combination Skin</p>
          <br>
          <br>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Clear Daily Soothing UV Defense SPF</strong><br>
                Protect your skin daily with this calming, broad-spectrum sunscreen. It hydrates and shields sensitive
                areas from UV exposure, helping prevent redness flare-ups and premature aging.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Gentle Cleanser</strong><br>
                Begin and end your day with this ultra-gentle cleanser that removes impurities without stripping
                moisture. It’s ideal for sensitive skin prone to redness, ensuring a clean and calm complexion.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phyto A+ Brightening Treatment Serum</strong><br>
                This advanced, oil-free serum visibly reduces redness and uneven skin tone while smoothing fine lines
                and rough texture. Its botanical blend, including azelaic acid, calms irritation and brightens your
                complexion.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phloretin CF by SkinCeuticals</strong><br>
                Combat oxidative stress and protect your skin from environmental damage with this potent antioxidant
                serum. Rich in vitamin C and phloretin, it helps minimize redness, supports collagen production, and
                brightens your skin.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phyto Corrective Gel</strong><br>
                Soothe and hydrate with this calming botanical gel designed for sensitive and mature skin. Infused with
                hyaluronic acid, cucumber, and thyme, it delivers a cooling effect that reduces visible redness and
                improves hydration.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phyto Corrective Essence Mist</strong><br>
                Instantly calm and refresh your skin anytime during the day. This lightweight mist strengthens the skin
                barrier, reduces redness, and provides immediate hydration to keep your skin feeling balanced and
                comfortable.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Redness Neutralizer</strong><br>
                Finish your routine with this advanced redness-reducing treatment. It contains biomimetic peptides and
                natural extracts to minimize inflammation triggers, helping to maintain long-term calmness and reinforce
                your skin’s natural defenses.
              </p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
